oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Buckman Quad in Ice
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Ice; Winter; Storms; Trees; Plough Library; Quadrangles (Courtyards)
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Trees all over Memphis sank under the weight of two inches of ice during the Ice Storm of 1994. The tree that stood in Buckman Quad was one of the victims. Plough Library can be seen in the background.
